# PKPassLibraryAddPassesStatus.didAddPasses

**Case**

A status that occurs when the user successfully adds one or more passes.

## Declaration

```swift
case didAddPasses
```

## Constants

- **PKPassLibraryAddPassesStatus.shouldReviewPasses**: A status that occurs when the app prompts the user to review the passes.
- **PKPassLibraryAddPassesStatus.didCancelAddPasses**: A status that occurs when the user cancels the addition of passes.
